---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="CYPERX.DEV // BLOG" activeNav="blog">

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════
       DARK VARIANT — blog-shard-feed
  ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="variant-dark bg-[#131313] text-[#e2e2e2] min-h-screen">
    <main class="relative pt-28 sm:pt-32 pb-16 sm:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto min-h-screen">
      <!-- Hero -->
      <section class="mb-16 sm:mb-24 relative">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-[#39FF14] mb-4 tracking-[0.5em] uppercase">[ STATUS: INTERCEPTING_SIGNAL_STREAM ]</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter italic uppercase glitch-text leading-none">SYSTEM<br/>ENTROPY<br/>LOGS</h1>
        <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 max-w-xl text-base sm:text-lg text-[#e2e2e2]/80 border-l-4 border-[#FF51FA] pl-6 italic">Raw data sharded from the core. These are the fragments of a dying architecture, rendered for your optical intake. No filters. No safety.</div>
      </section>

      <!-- Blog Feed -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 sm:gap-12 lg:gap-y-32">
        <!-- Shard 1: Featured -->
        <article class="md:col-span-8 group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-[#39FF14]/20 blur-xl group-hover:bg-[#39FF14]/40 transition-colors"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-[#2a2a2a] shard-clip-1 melt-effect border-l-8 border-[#39FF14] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-8">
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 aspect-video overflow-hidden relative">
                <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500 scale-110 group-hover:scale-100" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuApzEjhKLLfzadUq_evKE5oJfTQGtg_Lz2jMczC3Jx6GydACaRM6ZL3AZCPFv6_fYDnBI2gyBBh83YvHXQsyzJOr9NdtyJw0-frK18ljtLTmoKPimd5IKDDDHD6KekU5l7zRO4RTCHCjNMKNzgwaHLqQY_V1GcIh5vM-woQIU16SyVVo1MJL3_KOgqcgAnko4YhX3iO1Y_UtHgma8So47mjfrT9XTEMEMmB2xTL40D8OnGh5tbnL48ny-K-ZEYtfnHMJdKQUfe_X4c" alt="Cyber grid" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#39FF14]/10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                  <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#FF51FA] mb-2">SIGNAL_STRENGTH: 88% // 2024.08.12</div>
                  <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-none mb-4 sm:mb-6 group-hover:text-[#39FF14] transition-colors">THE_LIQUID_INFRASTRUCTURE_MYTH</h2>
                  <p class="text-[#baccb0] mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-sm sm:text-base">Decentralized protocols aren't enough. We need architectures that melt when the pressure rises and reform in the void.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[10px] border-t border-[#e2e2e2]/20 pt-4">
                  <span>ENTROPY: 0.44</span>
                  <span class="text-[#39FF14]">READ_FRAGMENT_&gt;&gt;</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Shard 2: Sidebar -->
        <article class="md:col-span-4 group">
          <div class="bg-[#0e0e0e] shard-clip-2 p-6 sm:p-8 border-r-4 border-[#FF51FA] h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e2e2e2]/50 mb-4">LOG_ENTRY_409</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 italic leading-tight">NEURAL_GHOSTS_IN_THE_CACHE</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#e2e2e2]/50">What remains when you flush the memory? The artifacts of past sessions still vibrate in the low-level registers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12 flex flex-col gap-2 font-mono text-[10px]">
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span>SYSTEM_HEALTH</span><span class="text-red-400">DEGRADED</span></div>
              <div class="w-full bg-[#353535] h-1"><div class="bg-red-400 w-1/3 h-full animate-pulse"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Shard 3: Middle Split -->
        <article class="md:col-start-2 md:col-span-5 group">
          <div class="bg-[#393939] shard-clip-3 p-6 sm:p-10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl">leak_add</span></div>
            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] bg-[#39FF14] text-black inline-block px-2 mb-4 sm:mb-6">UNSTABLE_DATA</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black uppercase mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-none">VOID_ROUTING: BEYOND_TCP</h3>
            <p class="text-[#e2e2e2] mb-6 sm:mb-8 italic text-sm sm:text-base">Packet loss is a feature, not a bug. If the data isn't missing fragments, was it ever even real?</p>
            <button class="w-full py-3 sm:py-4 border border-[#39FF14] text-[#39FF14] uppercase font-black hover:bg-[#39FF14] hover:text-black transition-all text-sm">SYNC_WITH_VOID</button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Shard 4: Landscape -->
        <article class="md:col-span-6 group">
          <div class="bg-[#2a2a2a] shard-clip-1 p-6 sm:p-8 flex gap-4 sm:gap-6 items-start border-b-4 border-[#AC89FF]">
            <div class="w-16 sm:w-24 h-16 sm:h-24 flex-shrink-0 bg-[#353535] border border-[#e2e2e2]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#39FF14] text-2xl sm:text-4xl animate-pulse">memory</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#AC89FF] mb-1">STABLE_DIFFUSION_VOICE</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-2 sm:mb-3">AI_SENSORY_OVERLOAD</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#e2e2e2]/50">Exploring the limits of synthetic perception in high-entropy environments.</p>
              <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 flex gap-2 sm:gap-4">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-[#1f1f1f] text-[8px] font-mono">#SYNTH</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-[#1f1f1f] text-[8px] font-mono">#SIGNAL</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Shard 5: Vertical Tower -->
        <article class="md:col-span-3 md:row-span-2 group">
          <div class="bg-[#0e0e0e] shard-clip-2 p-4 sm:p-6 border-t-8 border-[#c600c6] h-full flex flex-col gap-6 sm:gap-8">
            <div class="h-40 sm:h-64 bg-[#1f1f1f] relative">
              <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBROVdxHOc1mziCO1MtK2GrSuSCX8SbrCFYEfNa7vMjSCBWyk2PsiQR2yjn-w-zR8wYEgJMjA3rcHMmEN7MZmrSRQyrHREVVKziGVWSk3mbgWX57V12J-6hj_xzKO03HoyqURrs7fcFYeq5usPa0tjAy20ZKlp_tY3QmD7xpiv8DNAV24nyzXxHQXDnsyF269l5Z6eQF2gea8OcacLkPwa3qDB38ie7WhfPE-mbTWqnyumqjn34oqk3T_7OhTzLgOSYPR8OK-BuZVc" alt="Circuit board" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-black uppercase mb-3 sm:mb-4 italic">HARDWARE_SHAMANISM</h3>
              <p class="text-xs font-mono text-[#e2e2e2]/60 leading-relaxed">Treating silicon like sacred bone. The ritual of the overclock. Why we sacrifice GPUs to the gods of the frame rate.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto pt-6 sm:pt-8 border-t border-white/5 font-mono text-[10px] text-[#FF51FA]">READ_TIME: 44_CYCLES</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Shard 6: Grid Filler -->
        <article class="md:col-span-8 group">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-[#2a2a2a] p-4 sm:p-6 shard-clip-1 hover:skew-y-1 transition-transform">
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] mb-2 opacity-50 uppercase">Fragment_881</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold uppercase text-sm sm:text-base">CRYPTO_BREACH_LOGS</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#2a2a2a] p-4 sm:p-6 shard-clip-3 hover:-skew-y-1 transition-transform">
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] mb-2 opacity-50 uppercase">Fragment_223</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold uppercase text-sm sm:text-base">THE_GHOST_PROTOCOL</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2 bg-[#39FF14] p-1 font-black italic uppercase text-center text-black text-sm">VIEW_OLDER_SIGNAL_INTERCEPTS_...</div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>


  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════
       LIGHT VARIANT — blog-bleached-shards
  ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="variant-light bg-white text-[#131313] min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">
    <main class="pt-28 sm:pt-32 pb-16 sm:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="relative mb-16 sm:mb-24">
        <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-[#FF51FA]/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-9xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none mb-4 glitch-text">
          SIGNAL<br/>DECAY_
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-[#FF51FA] font-bold">
          <span>STATUS: OVERLOAD</span>
          <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-[#FF51FA]"></span>
          <span>ENTROPY: 99.9%</span>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Sharded Blog Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-y-12 md:gap-y-0">
        <!-- Article 1: Large Bleached Shard -->
        <article class="md:col-span-8 md:translate-x-4 z-10 group">
          <div class="bg-[#ebebeb] p-1 transition-all group-hover:bg-[#39FF14] duration-75" style="clip-path:polygon(10% 0, 100% 5%, 90% 100%, 0 85%)">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12 relative overflow-hidden" style="clip-path:polygon(10% 0, 100% 5%, 90% 100%, 0 85%)">
              <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-mono text-[10px] text-[#AC89FF]">#001_NULL</div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black uppercase mb-6 leading-tight">Architecture of a Fractal Void</h2>
              <div class="aspect-video mb-8 bg-[#f0f0f0] overflow-hidden relative">
                <img class="w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" alt="Abstract white fractal geometry with neon highlights" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuABaHfAk6ZL8rlbdj2z85oA3AAlZqV5ymu1cYf7rklSxuD81hrwGB8nglSjBnHAsDdwqbZPEQ98W0TvLb6XYAwcje2aDpBfl1idaz3YUbn-pfv8P785qxBMoNNSKexCoAXOlrKClv9AbttQOkCH-p21FoIghNGZU3oMmrCZEabvbPSKi3pX_aEsUsv7nsxza0j50ZyqllWzFbZS5Lr784tcPSpYaRQw2-_Bqgc0vktPZjqTNwrl2zVqnYmCDNkl22sD7OD1jIEU7CQ"/>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                The screen bleaches. The data blooms. We are no longer observing the interface; we are decomposing within its architecture.
              </p>
              <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[#39FF14] group-hover:text-[#FF51FA]" href="#">
                READ_MORE <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- Article 2: Small Overlapping Shard -->
        <article class="md:col-span-5 md:-translate-y-24 md:-ml-12 z-20 group">
          <div class="bg-[#FF51FA] p-1 transition-all duration-75 hover:skew-y-2" style="clip-path:polygon(5% 5%, 90% 0, 100% 95%, 0% 100%)">
            <div class="bg-white p-6" style="clip-path:polygon(5% 5%, 90% 0, 100% 95%, 0% 100%)">
              <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-start">
                <span class="bg-[#FF51FA] text-white text-[10px] font-mono px-2 py-1">CRITICAL_FAIL</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] opacity-40">2024.05.12</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-4">Toxic White: The Visual Frequency of Panic</h3>
              <p class="text-sm mb-6 opacity-70">
                Research into high-luminance UI and its effect on the lizard brain. Why we crave the blinding light of the void.
              </p>
              <div class="w-full h-32 bg-[#f8f8f8] overflow-hidden">
                <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" alt="Neon pink light leaking through white shards" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAS09UON0o8JlPrpg5BPyuGdEQddPzmVPmbCP306mNAxAOSauwHNcgVj4NPi-kK6ndAVtHP9tSmS5s1_Q0I8jFzSd6ZXyIDDyu-7RWGOo8c2003fdnItmosvVQ_N7uWR9KWpOGHBM55EW2gVwM6sjWHrUxNht5m6O1eTWPjSYiAdL94k7NYa4VoAaN9LKdD2oLQ2bIcIlED0CEG61KiTNo8a0-BnSshDUOG00iaQ0sjLNwwFKpKv1nEBqU2umV--fgyYK98wqimKxE"/>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- Article 3: Lateral Shard -->
        <article class="md:col-span-7 md:col-start-6 md:-translate-y-48 z-10 group">
          <div class="bg-[#AC89FF] p-1 transition-all duration-75 hover:bg-[#39FF14]" style="clip-path:polygon(0 15%, 95% 0, 100% 85%, 5% 100%)">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8" style="clip-path:polygon(0 15%, 95% 0, 100% 85%, 5% 100%)">
              <div class="md:w-1/3 aspect-square bg-[#f0f0f0]">
                <img class="w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-screen brightness-150" alt="Digital glitch pattern in green and white" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC8fX4aczWDeOkXirR5PLH40fY6wah1nQptqyaUajlL75x-ZWxKRFUfl8SN5tF7-3uD2403BBsV3ndVLUBndTODa_ggLYRwVxtr87O7Y0ipSC4qS6Solv0JyB48mc-QfsCTfASIFJirb9u-_a-LKTqY1dxEp1uJU4r0lxlGw6vSNhk8xl_JsuE4el_8q6xy_-NrLHYnQ8jaJabU26dlKef2a-jOnBgytdj1t83EXGmsaG3v_T0b9HWfEQDTPuZpBCWtox5wgi7Of6Y"/>
              </div>
              <div class="md:w-2/3">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase mb-4">Melted Interactivity</h3>
                <p class="text-base mb-6 opacity-80">
                  Breaking the standard 12-column grid to find the liquid state of digital information.
                </p>
                <button class="border-2 border-[#131313] px-6 py-2 font-black uppercase hover:bg-[#131313] hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  EXPLORE_NODE
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- Floating Sidebar: Acid Toggle -->
        <aside class="md:col-span-3 md:fixed md:right-12 md:top-64 z-40">
          <div class="p-6 bg-[#ebebeb] border-r-4 border-[#39FF14]" style="clip-path:polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 95% 100%, 5% 95%)">
            <h4 class="font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-[#FF51FA]">SYSTEM_CONTROL</h4>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center group cursor-pointer">
                <span class="font-black text-sm uppercase group-hover:text-[#39FF14]">GLITCH_FEED</span>
                <div class="w-10 h-5 bg-[#39FF14] p-1">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-black"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center group cursor-pointer">
                <span class="font-black text-sm uppercase group-hover:text-[#FF51FA] line-through">SAFETY_NET</span>
                <div class="w-10 h-5 bg-[#f0f0f0] p-1">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#131313]/20"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-[#131313]/10">
              <p class="font-mono text-[9px] leading-tight opacity-50">
                WARNING: HIGH FREQUENCY VISUALS MAY CAUSE SENSORY SYNESTHESIA. PROCEED INTO THE WHITE.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
      <!-- Terminal Section -->
      <section class="mt-12 md:-mt-24 p-6 sm:p-8 bg-[#131313] text-white max-w-2xl" style="clip-path:polygon(10% 0, 100% 5%, 90% 100%, 0 85%)">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#39FF14]"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-tighter">REMOTE_TERMINAL_ACCESS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-mono text-sm text-[#39FF14]/80 space-y-1">
          <p>&gt; LOADING ENTROPY_LOGS...</p>
          <p>&gt; STABLE BEYOND VOID [TRUE]</p>
          <p>&gt; SIGNAL BLOOM DETECTED</p>
          <p class="animate-pulse">&gt; _</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>


  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════
       EXTREME VARIANT — blog-shard-breach-dark-extreme
  ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="variant-extreme bg-[#050505] text-white min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden" style="cursor:crosshair">
    <main class="relative pt-28 sm:pt-32 pb-16 sm:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto min-h-screen">
      <!-- Fractal Underlay -->
      <div class="fixed inset-0 x-fractal-bg -z-10"></div>
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <header class="mb-20 sm:mb-32 space-y-8 relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-64 h-64 bg-[#8eff71]/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-[10rem] font-black tracking-tighter x-vibrating-text uppercase leading-none">
          DATA<br/>LOGS_0x0
        </h1>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 sm:gap-8 text-[#8eff71] font-mono text-sm sm:text-lg">
          <span class="animate-ping h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#8eff71]"></span>
          <span class="tracking-[0.3em] sm:tracking-[0.5em] font-black text-[#ff51fa]">SYSTEM_INFILTRATION_CRITICAL</span>
          <span class="opacity-40 italic">// ENTROPY: 99.98% // SECTOR: VOID_NULL</span>
        </div>
      </header>
      <!-- Shard Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Featured Shard -->
        <article class="md:col-span-9 group relative mb-12 sm:mb-20">
          <div class="absolute -inset-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#8eff71] via-[#ff51fa] to-[#ac89ff] blur-[100px] opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-[#191919] border-4 border-[#8eff71]/50 x-shard-melt-intense shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(142,255,113,0.3)] overflow-hidden x-glitch-hover">
            <div class="x-shard-inner-fractal"></div>
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[21/9]">
              <img alt="Abstract neon geometric structures" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale invert contrast-[1.5] brightness-[1.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:invert-0 transition-all duration-1000 scale-150 group-hover:scale-100" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBqEcMx3GLdKip5cD62YHedg03UpAHh0pnasq_xqIGwoCN9K6_vBn7DF8OKePusRs9Rw82DvVwJqBEKPzBIrGEU2BFo5TLpjNfEWZX5D1r_FTDcX24FGXGlYK0Lx-mKsKSe7XuAcivpt4XcWItRFAVp0jYZhG_wIqD88AtJnaqPHQwZuAjozdKxb8o5czCYBGllicBvODVZfpxvzLufNN-Y59v3WzCbZTGgenDchuYcuJpdSE-L2UkLNElIftV7AQRkeX7J0VXDKV8"/>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/40 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-8 sm:bottom-20 left-6 sm:left-12 right-6 sm:right-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter x-vibrating-text group-hover:text-[#8eff71]">
                  NEURAL_MELTDOWN_PROTOCOL_v4
                </h2>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 sm:p-12 pt-4 space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 relative z-10">
              <p class="text-white text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold leading-tight max-w-3xl italic tracking-tight">
                "THE BOUNDARIES BETWEEN SILICON AND SOUL ARE DISSOLVING. WE ARE THE LEAK IN THE REALITY PIPELINE."
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12">
                <button class="bg-[#8eff71] text-[#0d6100] px-8 sm:px-16 py-4 sm:py-6 font-black text-base sm:text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all x-shard-1 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(142,255,113,0.8)]">
                  DECRYPT_VOID
                </button>
                <span class="text-[#ff51fa] font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm animate-pulse">0x88FF112 // HASH_CORRUPTED</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- Sidebar Shards -->
        <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-8 sm:space-y-16">
